---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy & Terms" description="Privacy policy and license terms for Chelydra Labs.">
  <section class="container" style="padding: 4rem 0; max-width: 680px;">
    <h1 style="border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 0.8rem; font-family: var(--mono); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.02em; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      Privacy &amp; Terms
    </h1>
    
    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      Chelydra Labs believes in minimal, privacy-first software. This page outlines the data practices and licensing terms for the <code>chelydra.dev</code> website.
    </p>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border: none; padding: 0;">
        1. No Cookies &amp; No Tracking
      </h2>
      <p>
        This website does not set any cookies, does not collect personal identifiers, and does not use any third-party analytic trackers (like Google Analytics). You can navigate the site in full privacy. Because we do not use tracking cookies, you will not see a cookie consent banner here.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border: none; padding: 0;">
        2. Server Logs &amp; IP Addresses
      </h2>
      <p>
        When you access this website, our web server and hosting infrastructure (Railway) automatically collect standard network connection log data, which includes your IP address, web browser type, and the pages you visit. This data is collected strictly for security auditing, system troubleshooting, and DDoS prevention. This processing is based on our legitimate interest (GDPR Article 6(1)(f)) and the logs are rotated out automatically in accordance with standard infrastructure maintenance cycles.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border: none; padding: 0;">
        3. Software Distribution via GitHub
      </h2>
      <p>
        Our projects are hosted and distributed on GitHub. When you download a release binary or view our code repositories, you are redirected to GitHub's servers. These interactions are subject to <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a> and Terms of Service.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border: none; padding: 0;">
        4. MIT License Limitation of Liability
      </h2>
      <p>
        All software projects published by Chelydra Labs are licensed under the MIT License unless specified otherwise. The software is provided <strong>"as is"</strong>, without warranty of any kind, express or implied, including but not limited to the warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and noninfringement. In no event shall the authors or copyright holders be liable for any claim, damages, or other liability.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; border: none; padding: 0;">
        5. Contact
      </h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions regarding these terms, you can contact us at the address provided on our <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
